items.headline: Welcome to the Spider-Man Wiki!
items.desc: Spider-Man Wiki is all about the web-slinging, wall-crawling superhero Spider-Man! Everything from the films, the comics, the video games can be found right here!  We are currently in need of more users, so feel free to come on over and help us create a wiki that fans of The Amazing Spider-Man can be proud of!

items.name: Spider Rider Center
items.title: Spider Rider Center
items.headline: Welcome to Spider Riders Wikia
items.desc: The Spider Riders Wikia is a community site dedicated to the science fiction novel series Spider Riders and the animated series it inspired. If you are a fan of this series, or even if you're just curious about it, then this is the place for you! Come explore our content and help us expand this database... or join us in discussion about the novels, the animated series, or Spider Riders in general. All are welcome!

items.name: Amazing Spider-Man Wiki
items.title: Amazing Spider-Man Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Amazing Spider-Man Wiki!
items.desc:
Welcome to the wiki all about the new Amazing Spider-Man film franchise!

The Amazing Spider-Man is a reboot of the Spider-Man films. The film is directed by Marc Webb. Andrew Garfield, Emma Stone, Rhys Ifans and Denis Leary star in the film. The film was released on July 3, 2012 and gained the place of fourth-highest grossed film of 2012, losing only to Ice Age 4: Continental Drift, The Dark Knight Rises and finally, another Marvel Entertainment-produced film, The Avengers.

The Amazing Spider-Man 2 is the upcoming sequel to 2012's The Amazing Spider-Man. It is scheduled for release on May 2, 2014.

items.name: Ultimate Spider-Man Animated Series Wiki
items.title: Ultimate Spider-Man Animated Series Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to The Daily Bugle!
items.desc:
Welcome to The Daily Bugle! We are the newspaper wikia that gives off the information for the Ultimate Spider-Man series. Ultimate Spider-Man is an American television series created by Stan Lee and Steve Ditko for Disney XD. This show is based on the Marvel's Ultimate Spider-Man comics. The series follows the life of the young teenager Peter Parker, who is the amazing hero Spider-Man to understand and reach his maximum potential powers by joining the agency S.H.I.E.L.D. and forming a team of super heroes to defeat the powerful supervillains.

Here at the The Daily Bugle, we strive to document everything about the series. If you want to share your knowledge and passion for the show, join us today. After all, this wiki can be edited by anyone, including you!

items.headline: Bienvenidos a Wiki Ultimate Spider-Man
items.desc: Spider-Man (nombre real Peter Parker) No sólo es el joven Parker tienen que luchar con su cotidiana lucha contra el crimen y la intimidación a través del constante carrera, él también tiene que enfrentarse a su mayor desafío de la escuela pero de altura! Por encima de todo eso, Nick Fury, director de S.H.I.E.L.D, le ha dado acceso a tecnología de S.H.I.E.L.D y un equipo de jóvenes adolescentes super-héroes para ayudar en su misión para derrotar a super-poderosos criminales.
